        <h1>{{ sessionName }}</h1>
        <h2>Speaker: <b>{{ speakerName }}</b></h2>
        <p class="lead">This site brings together to great platforms for web development.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <p>Angular JS is the leading JavaScript-based client framework for web development.</p>
            <p>ASP.NET MVC remains Microsoft's prefered web development framework and HTML delivery platform</p>
